        <mxCell id="legend" parent="1" vertex="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=4;" value="Legend&#10;──▶ solid  = code-verified pip dependency (import + pinned in pyproject/requirements)&#10;┄┄▶ dashed = intended end-state, NOT yet wired in code&#10;Purple dashed node = shared operator toolkit (not a pip library).&#10;Note: version skew on wegofwd-llm (pramana v0.1.1 vs Mentible v0.1.3). wegofwd-llm docs also list StudyBuddy_OnDemand &amp; Thittam as wegofwd-llm consumers (shown here via orchestration; their llm edges not drawn). wegofwd-expenses is a further wegofwd-llm consumer (billclassify/billextract), also not drawn.&#10;wegofwd-video (ADR-026; pkg v1.0.0, consumers pin git tag v0.1.2) is used by pramana &amp; kathai-chithiram; Mentible planned.&#10;wegofwd-orchestration: a dependency-free operator toolkit (triage → taskforge → critique-gate) that orchestrates the product repos and supplies the progress_inflight seam used by StudyBuddy_OnDemand &amp; Thittam's nightly progress generators; it consumes none of the shared libraries.">
